        "caption": "Tailwind CSS Workshop\n\nClean designs. Faster workflow. Better-looking projects.\nIf you’ve ever spent way too long fixing your CSS, it’s time to switch things up. Join our Tailwind CSS Workshop and learn how to build modern, responsive UIs in a quicker and smarter way.\n\n🎤 Speaker: Chow Ying Tong\n📅 Date: 23rd April 2026\n⏰ Time: 7:45 PM – 10:15 PM\n📍 Venue: Agmo Space, Faculty of Creative Multimedia, MMU Cyberjaya\n\nIn this session, you’ll get to:\n• Understand how Tailwind CSS actually works\n• Build responsive layouts without the usual struggle\n• Style components faster and more efficiently\n• Pick up tips to make your UI look clean and consistent\n\nLess time fighting CSS, more time creating designs you’re proud of ✨\nPull up and level up your front-end game!\n\nRegister here: https://luma.com/svwsrs0h",
